something out of a dream."

01:31:06.610 --> 01:31:08.420
"Nothing more or less..."

01:31:08.440 --> 01:31:10.780
"than a breathtaking view."

01:31:10.800 --> 01:31:15.190
Words like "tomorrow"
or "future" or "fate",

01:31:15.210 --> 01:31:18.990
no matter how far they extend their hands,

01:31:19.010 --> 01:31:22.800
we breathe, we dream, we raise our love

01:31:22.820 --> 01:31:26.940
in a timeless land
that is far out of reach.

01:31:26.960 --> 01:31:30.610
Even the second, hour hands of the clock.

01:31:30.630 --> 01:31:34.640
They look at us sideways
as they tick and tock.

01:31:34.660 --> 01:31:39.500
How I hope to have
forever to spend this life,

01:31:39.520 --> 01:31:41.920
no-all future lives

01:31:41.940 --> 01:31:49.740
right here in this world with you!

01:32:42.500 --> 01:32:43.960
Huh?

01:32:44.420 --> 01:32:45.990
Why am I here?

01:32:47.280 --> 01:32:50.090
What am I... doing?

01:33:08.690 --> 01:33:09.800
U-uh!

01:33:14.430 --> 01:33:18.130
