01:33:20.720 --> 01:33:23.500
I'm always searching for something.

01:33:23.520 --> 01:33:27.130
This... feeling has consumed me...

01:33:27.150 --> 01:33:29.110
for some time.

01:33:30.410 --> 01:33:32.450
The reason I applied for this position-

01:33:32.470 --> 01:33:33.990
The landscapes people live in-

01:33:34.010 --> 01:33:35.940
To build a city's landscape-

01:33:35.960 --> 01:33:38.900
Even Tokyo. It might vanish too one day.

01:33:38.920 --> 01:33:43.310
And so, I wanna make landscapes
that-how should I put this?

01:33:43.330 --> 01:33:46.800
That can continue to warm peoples' hearts.

01:33:48.460 --> 01:33:50.750
That bad? How many does that make it?

01:33:50.770 --> 01:33:53.500
- I've stopped counting.
- Doesn't sound too promising.

01:33:53.520 --> 01:33:56.090
